Title: Fix translated error if multisite url of site connection is invalid
Level: 1
Component: multisite
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p23
Date: 1617882905
Class: fix

If you used german language and tried to enter an invalid multisite url for a
site connection, it was stated, that the url has to end with "/check_mk". The
message now shows the correct expected input "/check_mk/".
